# API Test Collection

## 1. Role Management

### Create Role
POST http://localhost:5000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "description": "Administrator role"
}

### Get All Roles
GET http://localhost:5000/api/roles

### Get Role By ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/roles/{roleId}

### Update Role
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/roles/{roleId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Moderator",
  "description": "Moderator role"
}

### Delete Role (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/roles/{roleId}

---

## 2. User Management

### Create User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "avatarUrl": "https://i.sstatic.net/l60Hf.png",
  "role": null
}

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### Get User By ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/{userId}

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/{userId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe Updated"
}

### Delete User (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/{userId}

### Enable User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/enable
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "john_doe"
}

### Disable User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/disable
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "username": "john_doe"
}
